\v 31 Pharaoh will see them, and he will be comforted over all of his hordes killed by \add the\add* sword, Pharaoh and all of his army,” ⸤declares⸥\f + \fr 32:31 \ft Literally “declaration of” \f* the Lord Yahweh. 
